ts you\u2019re looking for.\r\n\r\nWith Google Romance, you can: \r\n\r\nUpload your profile \u2013 tell the world who you are, or, more to the point, who you\u2019d like to think you are, or, even more to the point, who you want others to think you are. \r\nSearch for love in all (or at least a statistically significant majority of) the right places with Soulmate Search, our eerily effective psychographic matchmaking software. \r\nEndure, via our Contextual Dating option, thematically appropriate multimedia advertising throughout the entirety of your free date. \r\nLearn more: Take the Tour, Press Release, FAQ", "imagename": "7cce707931864cbcb29fea4566ecbe82.jpg", "infoid": 16066, "category": "technology_google", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["google"]}, {"url": "http://lifehacker.com/software/windows/lh-top-10--free-windows-downloads-248303.php", "title": "10\u5927Windows\u4e0a\u7684\u514d\u8d39\u8f6f\u4ef6\u4e0b\u8f7d", "tags": "", "name": "diglog", "posttime": "2007-04-01 13:56:43", "ip": "221.14.253.130", "mark": 9, "note": "\u5305\u62ec\u4e86FireFox,Launchy,Paint.NET,GAIM,foobar2000\u7b49,\u8fd9\u4e9b\u8f6f\u4ef6\u53ef\u4ee5\u4f7f\u4f60\u7684\u64cd\u4f5c\u7cfb\u7edf\u66f4\u4e3a\u5065\u58ee\u3001\u66f4\u4e3a\u5f3a\u5927,\u514d\u8d39\u7684\u597d\u4e1c\u897f,\u8d76\u5feb\u6765\u4e0b\u8f7d\u3002", "imagename": "", "infoid": 16065, "category": "technology_software", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": null}, {"url": "http://www.freeproxysite.com/", "title": "\u4e00\u4e2a\u56fd\u5916\u514d\u8d39\u7684\u4ee3\u7406\u7f51\u7ad9 Free Proxy Site", "tags": "Free Proxy Site ", "name": "diglog", "posttime": "2007-04-01 13:47:38", "ip": "221.14.253.130", "mark": 8, "note": "Free Proxy Site is the place to find a 100% free anonymous web proxy site that is fast and easy to use. Free Proxy Site links to 263 working sites that will in